name: #4 The misty morning
description:
This is a panorama photo of my ”misty morning” collection (7 photos of 1/1 edition). I got up early in the morning to enjoy the nature and the sunrise. Went to a lake near Karlskrona, Sweden and i faced this beautiful landscape. The mist, the lake, the reflections and of course the fall colors. The scenery that brings calmness in your soul and it brings you near nature.
1/1 edition of each photo.
